Interface ITaskVisitor

All Known Subinterfaces:
TaskVisitor
All Known Implementing Classes:
CountByStateVisitor, CsvFlatTaskVisitor, PlainTextFlatTaskVisitor
public interface ITaskVisitor
Base visitor interface over task export record variants.

Provides type-specific visit methods for each record implementation, enabling pattern matching on task state. Includes an optional complete() hook for batch traversal completion.
